data.description: Complete info: http://3857windingtwigdr.CanBYours.com - **IN CONTRACT** Located in the Abbie Trails sub-division of Canal Winchester, this lovely 3BR, 2BA ranch is a bargain that just can't be beat. Built in 2006, this immaculate gem of a home offers an open floor plan with a large combined Living Room / Kitchen area boasting a beautiful fireplace and large Dining area for family gatherings and relaxation. The Master bedroom features a large walk-in closet and private bath, while the Den is just enough away from it all to allow for quiet time when needed. The attached 2-car garage is partially finished and the low-maintenance masonry/vinyl exterior means less time spent caring for and more time available to admire and enjoy this fantastic deal. It's move-in ready and immediately available. If you've been looking for that perfect bargain in this market, look no further...this is THE ONE. Don't miss out on this FANTASTIC property at this GREAT price. CALL ME TODAY for your personal showing. Columbus MLS# 211026149. Lancaster MLS# 9913413. Groveport-Madison Local Schools.
